## Permissions

|      ID      |           Description           |                            Notes                            |
|:------------:|:-------------------------------:|:-----------------------------------------------------------:|
| basic_access |       Can access this app       |           All line members should have this role            |
|   manager    | Can create and manage evictions | Role to create/edit evictions and access archived evictions |

